{"tid":524440,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚牛丸愛好者","createTime":"2018-01-09T14:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T11:52:31.000Z","uid":161649,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"13be8d14799e10fe5a39a5a85436cc6eca4f765c","tid":524440,"uid":161649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:42:30.000Z","msg":"大家如果鍾意食牛丸<br />\n相信一定試過唔同種類嘅牛丸<br />\n講緊唔係乜野醬爆 黑椒果啲<br />\n一粒牛丸用唔同部位嘅肉打出黎 <br />\n口感真係可以差好遠<br />\n<br />\n我就好鍾情一種極爽口彈牙又重牛肉味嘅<br />\n買番嚟係淺灰色，滾水淥完變淺灰白色 <br />\n極極極彈牙<br />\n如圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/223419_b864bd110595ebb0584e734211ed3c53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F223419_b864bd110595ebb0584e734211ed3c53.png&h=a99f0359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但坊間好多都係類似打邊爐凍肉舖賣果隻<br />\n啡色 淥完都係啡灰咁 似貢丸色<br />\n如圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/223638_f9e690de7bad4ba72d59de631fa08429.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F223638_f9e690de7bad4ba72d59de631fa08429.png&h=9963b8e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講左咁耐<br />\n其實想話食唔番第一張圖隻牛丸<br />\n以前係呀媽買 當時住元朗 <br />\n所以早幾年試過搵 <br />\n去過嘉麗園 勝利牛丸 其他粉麵舖<br />\n都唔係果隻<br />\n呀媽又唔記得<br />\n我有次喺灣仔食左間麵檔 味道好似<br />\n買左一袋番去 都始終唔係同一種<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知我講緊邊種牛丸<br />\n口感真係好大分別<br />\n知唔知邊到可以買到<br />\n<br />\n如果咁好彩搵到 我請提供資料者一齊食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def275552327af3f021a258d82c6d69af778c2f2","tid":524440,"uid":161649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:50:23.000Z","msg":"冇人鍾意食牛丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻牛丸食過真係畢生難忘架。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a87a862e861a1c02d1ad814ca1edf26f09c3847","tid":524440,"uid":38761,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:53:47.000Z","msg":"似係勝利"},{"pid":"32243d0a963c38456e81ecd0af03ad6f9e51138f","tid":524440,"uid":161649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a87a862e861a1c02d1ad814ca1edf26f09c3847","tid":524440,"uid":38761,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:53:47.000Z","msg":"似係勝利"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:57:52.000Z","msg":"你又幾醒 張圖係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我去買時 完全唔同<br />\n顏色都唔係圖中咁所好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727a3f0dbf377f4531a640998bc94d127adc5743","tid":524440,"uid":10433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a87a862e861a1c02d1ad814ca1edf26f09c3847","tid":524440,"uid":38761,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:53:47.000Z","msg":"似係勝利"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:57:55.000Z","msg":"應該都係"},{"pid":"d384e330cae53ce24ce75e9852090405e6ec3ec6","tid":524440,"uid":99745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:59:38.000Z","msg":"我覺得南記個隻牛丸最好味"},{"pid":"71c1cd0469b01e6a9b5b54c1fed339bf589340f6","tid":524440,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T15:00:27.000Z","msg":"有邊間推介"},{"pid":"1494111d68131fcd1982d806e43aac8a09e807a7","tid":524440,"uid":104669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"黑椒牛筋丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc04c133b8c85286dc05e1c20a96ada498846708","tid":524440,"uid":97708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T16:07:26.000Z","msg":"勝利係幾好食 但未好食到真係會專登入去食<br />\n反而我鍾意食d有少少肥豬肉既牛丸"},{"pid":"9e6fb44036ae350081cc8f58bdc8e24881cae5f1","tid":524440,"uid":26553,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T16:13:53.000Z","msg":"有無係潮汕食過牛丸？ <br />\n女朋友係潮汕人帶過我返去食， 肉汁口感 屌打曬咩勝利嘉利苑果d ，真係推翻左我對牛丸既認識<br />\n<br />\n事後先知成90人仔一磅"},{"pid":"f12e60e0749be2d5658dbb1e0bba7c2d75319526","tid":524440,"uid":161649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e6fb44036ae350081cc8f58bdc8e24881cae5f1","tid":524440,"uid":26553,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T16:13:53.000Z","msg":"有無係潮汕食過牛丸？ <br />\n女朋友係潮汕人帶過我返去食， 肉汁口感 屌打曬咩勝利嘉利苑果d ，真係推翻左我對牛丸既認識<br />\n<br />\n事後先知成90人仔一磅"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T16:21:21.000Z","msg":"未去過<br />\n但灣仔食到好接近果間好似叫潮興 潮發咁上下名<br />\n唔知係咪潮汕人開呢<br />\n巴打你食果隻咩顏色？"},{"pid":"8bf0af98b01b6ece44fc08d76bbcaae1ea8f270c","tid":524440,"uid":161649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1494111d68131fcd1982d806e43aac8a09e807a7","tid":524440,"uid":104669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"黑椒牛筋丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T16:23:18.000Z","msg":"牛丸要有筋先彈牙<br />\n牛筋丸我都鍾意 <br />\n買唔到好食牛丸我就會食牛筋丸"},{"pid":"4c323c016cae830e73314a246dcbf37ba1927315","tid":524440,"uid":65530,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T16:25:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e1c1545180f7f00ee7f6c6a3cafb2853ac09ce8","tid":524440,"uid":62621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T18:32:14.000Z","msg":"元朗勝利係純牛肉 機器造<br />\n坊間果D一般會溝豬肉/添加劑<br />\n潮州手打純牛肉 係正好貴"},{"pid":"ecfd3d4261bd58eeaf44d4d6953cb776258ab1a8","tid":524440,"uid":161649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e1c1545180f7f00ee7f6c6a3cafb2853ac09ce8","tid":524440,"uid":62621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T18:32:14.000Z","msg":"元朗勝利係純牛肉 機器造<br />\n坊間果D一般會溝豬肉/添加劑<br />\n潮州手打純牛肉 係正好貴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0